</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>And what do you do then, <HI>William?</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Will.</SPEAKER>
<P>Alas! Sir, I go mourning many a Day,
