</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>Indeed that is true, <HI>William.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Will.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Then there are many comforting Scrip|tures,
