<HI>He will</HI> &s;atisfy the De&s;ires of all tho&s;e that fear him, <HI>and
the like.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>But what mu&s;t I do? which is the Way, an
