</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>You mu&s;t explain your &s;elf, <HI>William,</HI> I do
not under&s;tand you.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Will.</SPEAKER>
<P>Why, Sir, tho&s;e earne&s;t De&s;ires you have
