</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>You &s;urprize me a little, <HI>William.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Will.</SPEAKER>
<P>Be&s;ides, Sir, <HI>and't plea&s;e you,</HI> tho&s;e earne&s;t
