</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>La.</SPEAKER>
<P>I joyn'd with you, <HI>William;</HI> I don't know;
but if that be praying, I think I did pray.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Will.</SPEAKER>
<P>Thus God will move your Heart to pray
to him: and I be&s;eech your Wor&s;hip to read the
Scriptures; read them much, read them &s;eriou&s;ly,
