</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Bro.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>No, no;</HI> I am &s;ure I am not in the wrong.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sist.</SPEAKER>
<P>That's making your &s;elf Judge, Brother; I
