Well, <HI>&s;ays I,</HI> what then? What then! <HI>&s;ays &s;he.</HI> Why
<PB N="213" REF="219">
then I &s;hould be the happie&s;t Woman upon Earth&punc;
Methinks 'tis the melancholie&s;t Thing, <HI>continued
